<< /Alt (If you need to list other education information or training facilities use Section 9 - Remarks and provide the same detailed information as above. SECTION 8 - DAILY ACTIVITIES \rComplete only if you are age 18 years or older. Please tell us how your conditions affect your everyday life.  This will help us further understand your medical condition\(s\). 8. Do your medical conditions cause you to have difficulties doing any of the following? You should think  \r    about the difficulty you experience in performing these tasks alone and without assistance from other  \r    people or assistive devices. If other people or assistive devices help you perform a task or perform a task \r    for you because it would be difficult for you to perform the task without the assistance, choose "Yes". YES) /K 6 /P 1481 0 R /Pg 52 0 R /S /P >>
endobj
